      "purposeInStoryline": "This is the opening lesson of the unit. It anchors every subsequent lesson to a single, puzzling phenomenon drawn from Kenyan everyday life. By the end of this lesson students have posted their initial questions and predictions on the Driving Question Board, establishing the intellectual 'need to know' that will drive all 26 lessons in Sub-Strand 1.4. The review of atomic stability and valence electrons provides the conceptual foundation on which all bond types will be built.",
